    "_postman_id": "jobs-api-collection-2025",
    "name": "Scholarport Jobs API",
    "description": "# Jobs/Careers API Collection\n\nThis collection contains all endpoints for the Jobs/Careers API.\n\n## Setup Instructions\n\n1. **Set Base URL**: Update the `base_url` variable to your server URL\n2. **Get Auth Token**: Run \"Admin Login\" first to get JWT token\n3. **Token Auto-Save**: The login request automatically saves the token\n\n## Endpoint Categories\n\n### Public Endpoints (No Auth Required)\n- List Active Jobs\n- Get Job by Slug\n\n### Admin Endpoints (Auth Required)\n- List All Jobs (Admin)\n- Get Job by ID (Admin)\n- Create Job (Admin)\n- Update Job (Admin)\n- Delete Job (Admin)\n\n## Testing Flow\n\n1. Run \"List Active Jobs\" - Should return empty array initially\n2. Run \"Admin Login\" to get token\n3. Run \"Create Job\" to add a job\n4. Run \"List Active Jobs\" again - Should show the new job\n5. Run \"Get Job by Slug\" with the job's slug\n6. Run \"Update Job\" to modify the job\n7. Run \"Delete Job\" to remove it",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
